---
title: Prawn and Aubergine Curry with yoghurt drizzle and chilli coriander garnish
description: Meaty prawns and tender green beans make up the base of this creamy and slightly spiced curry. Topped with fresh chilli, crunchy peanuts and a cooling yoghurt drizzle, this dish can be tailored to all tastes and is sure to have something for everyone.
